      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that there are two sides but it feels like one side has a much better legal argument. like, isn't it more \"objective\" to just look at the original text instead of trying to guess what a bunch of people meant hundreds of years ago? seems like the \"activism\" side is just making stuff up to fit modern views.",
